headline: Federal Realty (FRT) Target Cut Slightly as Scotiabank Refreshes REIT Outlook
summary: Federal Realty Investment Trust (NYSE:FRT) is included among the 13 Best Dividend Kings to Buy in 2026. On January 14, Scotiabank trimmed its price target on Federal Realty Investment Trust (NYSE:FRT) to $113 from $114 and maintained an Outperform rating on the stock. The analyst said the firm is refreshing price targets across the US […]
